New comics from @peowstudio out this week!! Check out treasure hunting sci-fi adventure AEON 6 by @julesnaleb and journey to neomon inhabited Baby City in ICE CREAM & BEAST by @baby__iggy. 
Peow consistently puts out amazing comics full of gorgeous art and we’re happy to welcome these two new additions to our shelves that continue to dazzle our eyes.  Check them out this weekend! Or send us an email, if you want a copy reserved, to info@goshlondon.com

#comics #art #drawing #illustration #peowstudio #julesnaleb #iggycraig #adventure #scifi #loot

On Thursday 12th March 2020, the one and only Steven Appleby will be in store to launch DRAGMAN from @jonathancape!! “A delightfully witty and exciting graphic novel by one of Britain’s favourite artists

Dragman tells the story of August Crimp, a man who has superpowers when he puts on women’s clothes. August loves wearing a dress but is deeply ashamed of his compulsion and terrified of rejection should it ever come out. So he tells no one. Not even his wife. But then one day a little girl falls from the rooftop cafe at the Art Museum and August has no choice but to fly and save her – an event witnessed by hundreds of people.

And August Crimp’s life is never the same again.” @thelandofstevenappleby will be joining us between 7-9pm to celebrate the launch and sign copies of the new book!

#comics #art #drawing #illustration #dragman #jonathancape #stevenappleby #booklaunch #signing

We’re kicking off the launch of @odpomery’s brand new book BRITISH ICE right now! Owen will be with us until 9pm so pop down and get a copy signed!

If you can’t make it then you can still order a signed copy of the book from our web store.

#comics #art #drawing #illustration #topshelfcomics #owendpomery #booklaunch #arctic

This time next week, our monthly drawing session returns!! Our guest artists joining us this month are @takayo_aki, @rebecca_k_jones and Claude TC. So join us on Thursday 27th February for some intoxicated illustrating!! Drink and Draw is a monthly event hosted by Broken Frontier and Gosh! Comics. We invite our guest artists to the local pub where they'll each curate a drawing session over a few pints! Entry is free and everyone is welcome.

Drink and Draw will start at the store on Berwick Street at 6.30pm with an opportunity to meet and buy work from the featured creators. We will then migrate over to The Kings Arms on Poland Street at 7pm for a drawing session lead by the artists.

#comics #art #drawing #illustration #takayoakiyama #rebeccakjones #claudetc #brokenfrontier #cassart

This recent comic collection has been flying off the shelves! But don’t worry, there’s still plenty of great hardcover superhero books to choose from! Check out some of these fantastic comics that have replenished the shelves.

For any enquires, please email info@goshlondon.com

#comics #art #marvel #dc #superhero #batman #fantasticfour #neilgaiman #spiderman

Brand new issue of “The Hero Comics” from Snyder and Ditko productions now in stock! Issue 30 sees the return of Steve Ditko and Joe Gill’s Captain Atom, originally created for Charlton’s Space Adventures sixty years ago. This 48 pager is jam packed with more Ditko goodness so pick up a copy today! Or send an email to info@goshlondon.com to have it added to your standing order.

#comics #art #illustration #drawing #steveditko #snyderditko #captainatom #scifi

We just got in a humongous collection of comic gems!! Hundreds of omnibuses and hardbacks in great condition. So treat yourself to some classic superhero stories at bargain prices today!! #comics #art #marvel #dc #superhero #xmen #punisher #daredevil #avengers #captainamerica

We all thoroughly enjoyed Jonathan Hickman’s recent delve into Marvel’s favourite mutants, with X-Men stories House of X and Powers of X. Now that East of West has reached its end, Hickman hits us with his brand new creator owned sci-fi epic, DECORUM from @imagecomics. 
Check out some of the jaw-dropping art from artist Mike Huddleston! The first issue of Decorum lands on our shelves March 11th. If don’t want to miss out on this then add it to your standing order and email us at info@goshlondon.com

#comics #art #drawing #illustration #jonathanhickman #mikehuddleston #imagecomics #decorum #scifi #eastofwest #xmen

We’re celebrating our 34th birthday here at Gosh! Comics!! Had a lot of fun cracking open the vault to take a look at some of our very first leaflets, adverts, bookplates and other memories from 1986-2020.

#goshcomics #comics #art #illustration #comicshop #graphicdesign

After an incredible festival in Angoulême, it’d be a shame not to share some of the fantastic work that was on offer. Luckily, we were able to bring back some beautiful goodies, which you can purchase in our small press and self-published section!! Featuring work by:
Sammy Stein @sammystein_ 
Etienne Ciquier @frisson_tournesol 
Milo Manara @milomanara_official 
Yoshiharu Tsuge
Jon Chandler @newmancruise 
Makiko Furiuichi @makiko_furuichi 
So come down and grab yourself a little slice of @bdangouleme!! #comics #art #illustration #drawing #angouleme #angoulême #eurocomics #risograph #bandedessinee #bandedessinée #yoshiharutsuge #milomanara #bonehousebooks

Check out this delicious new print by @mais2_art we are now stocking! It’s exclusive to Gosh! so grab a copy in store or over on our web store!! #comics #art #illustration #drawing #print #printmaking #screenprinting #mais2 #alessandracriseo

On Friday 21st February, we welcome Owen D. Pomery to the store to launch his new Arctic-noir mystery, BRITISH ICE!! “Working for the British High Commission, Harrison Fleet is posted to a remote Arctic island, still, inexplicably, under British rule.

As he struggles to understand why, and what interests he is protecting, Harrison finds the dark shadow of the outpost’s founder cast heavily over the land and its community.

Caught between the hostile locals, the British government, and an unforgiving physical environment, he begins dragging dark secrets into the light, unaware of the tragic repercussions they will cause. All fat from the eyes and help of the world.” @odpomery will be with us from 7-9pm, so save the date and come along to meet Owen and get a copy of the book signed!! #comics #art #drawing #illustration #britishice #owendpomery #topshelf #booklaunch #arctic

Tonight! Emily Haworth-Booth is in the shop celebrating the launch of her new book from @pavilionchildrens. Join us from 7-9pm to chat and get copies signed!! #comics #art #illustration #drawing #childrensbooks #booksigning #booklaunch #environment #thelasttree #pavilion #ecofriendly

Isabel Greenberg’s brand new graphic novel, GLASS TOWN, is released today!! Isabel is making us a lovely window display to celebrate the occasion!

Glass Town, from @jonathancape, is based on the early lives of the Bronte siblings, infused with the imaginative flair and otherworldly fantasy that makes @isabel_greenberg’s work distinctively magical.

Join us at Gosh! tomorrow, Friday 7th February, from 7-9pm for the launch party of Glass Town! Meet Isabel and get a copy of the book signed!

#comics #art #drawing #livedrawing #illustration #graphicnovel #glasstown #jonathancape #booksigning #bronte #brontesisters

This Thursday we’re excited to be celebrating the launch of “The Last Tree”, the new children’s book from Emily Haworth-Booth!! @emilyhaworthbooth was the Observer/Comica/Cape graphic short story winner back in 2013. Her latest book emphasises the importance of community and protecting the environment.

Come join us to celebrate the launch on Thursday 6th February from 7-9pm.

#comics #art #drawing #booklaunch #illustration #childrensbooks #emilyhaworthbooth #pavilion #environment #ecofriendly #signing

We’ve just restocked some gorgeous prints by the amazing Kristyna Baczynski!! Check out all of the delicious designs now displaying on our walls, including the Gosh! exclusive screen print, “The Broad Street Pump”, signed by @kbaczynski herself!

#comics #art #illustration #printmaking #print #drawing #screenprinting #kristynabaczynski

We are incredibly excited to read new book by @isabel_greenberg next week! We are even more excited to welcome Isabel to the store to launch it! Isabel will be joining us on Friday 7th February from 7-9pm to sign copies of her new book. We even have some beautiful ‘Gosh! exclusive’ badges for every purchase of the book!! #comics #art #illustration #drawing #isabelgreenberg #jonathancape #signing #booklaunch

Thanks to everyone who came out to last night’s Drink and Draw! We had an absolute blast. Thank you to the amazing @brokenfrontier for co-hosting and of course to our wonderful guest artists @jamesalbon.illustration, @studio.lindsay and @peony__ ! Come check out their comics on our shelves now. We’ll see you next month!! #comics #art #drawing #illustration #brokenfrontier #goshbfdd #smallpresscomics #drinkanddraw #cassart #peonygent #lindsaypollock #jamesalbon

Tonight! We are incredibly excited to be joined by Bob Layton!! Layton is a writer, artist and editor who has worked with Marvel and DC. He’s worked on iconic Iron Man storylines serving as the inspiration for the MCU and is the co-creator of “Huntress” who will be featured in the upcoming Birds of Prey film. Check out some of his fantastic Iron Man covers!! Bob will be signing from 6-7pm.

And if that gets the creative juices flowing, perhaps you’ll be interested in our monthly drink and draw session tonight with Broken Frontier! Meet our wonderful guest artists Peony Gent, James Albon and Lindsay Pollock for a session of sipping and scribbles. Chat to our guests in the shop from 6.30pm or meet at the pub, “The Kings Arms” from 7pm.

#comics #art #illustration #drawing #boblayton #marvel #dc #birdsofprey #ironman #brokenfrontier #jamesalbon #lindsaypollock #peonygent #cassart

The first Drink & Draw of 2020 is this Thursday 30th January!! Come join our co-hosts Broken Frontier and ourselves, as we welcome James Albon, Peony Gent and Lindsay Pollock for a wonderful evening of doodling and drinking.

You can catch the artists in-store from 6.30pm where you’ll be able to purchase copies of their work. Then we’ll head to the Kings Arms on Poland Street from 7pm to start the fun.

#comics #art #drawing #illustration #jamesalbon #peonygent #lindsaypollock #brokenfrontier #cassart

There’s a fantastic selection of Studio Ghibli books on our shelves right now, including the brand new biography by Susan Napier, “Miyazakiworld: A Life in Art”. Exploring the life of the legendary filmmaker, Hayao Miyazaki, this is an essential read for any Ghibli fan.

We also have a lovely range of art books, showing off some of the beautiful art and behind the scenes knowledge of the classic animations.

If that’s not enough, we have “Starting Point”, a compilation of essays and more by Miyazaki; picture books of the movies; and the entire collection of the manga “Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind”. Phew! Come immerse yourself in the magical world of Miyazaki!

#studioghibli #anime #animation #manga #nausicaa #nausicaaofthevalleyofthewind #miyazaki #miyazakiworld #susannapier #totoro #ponyo

Breakdown Press start 2020 strong with their new release by Josephine M.K. Edwards! Check out Will o’ the Wisp by @j.m.k.e on our shelves now. “A ghoulish orb named ‘The Will- O’-The-Wisp’ flickers from the wick of Earth’s lantern in the midst of a barren void. The glimmer offers salvation to the hopeless, wayward traveller in the form of a point of reference. Disguised as The Northern Star or a guardian angel, the bioluminescent ghost is born from the oxidation of phosphine (PH3), diphosphane (P2H4) and methane (CH4), which is released from the decay of organic matter. Like a mosquito to a zapper, the hopeful traveller is drawn towards the glowing siren, who hovers over deep bogs, swamps and marshes. Here the traveller’s journey concludes, feeding the ghostly light.” #comics #art #illustration #breakdownpress #jkme #friendsinthedungeon #drawing

Absolutely blown away “J&K”, John Pham’s new graphic novel from Fantagraphics. Not only do you follow the adventures of Jay and Kay in this fabulously colourful 144 page hardcover, but collect their actual belongings! J&K is bursting with bonus goodies. Included with the book are collectible trading cards, a mini zine (even with its own inserts of course), a sticker sheet, a fold out poster/map and, most incredibly, a 5” inch vinyl single!! Come check out this delightful package of comics goodness for yourself!

#comics #illustration #art #graphicnovel #drawing #fantagraphics

The future of the X-Men begins here! Check out this fantastic hardcover collecting all of Jonathan Hickman’s latest mutant stories, “House of X” and “Powers of X”. If you’re a X-Men fan, then this is one event story you do not want to miss.
